notes:
Two things to note here:
1. The game will not launch until you go to the binaries folder, delete Launcher.exe, and rename BorderlandsGOTY.exe to Launcher.exe;
2. Disabling Esync is *required* on some systems in order for the game to run. To do so, "PROTON_NO_ESYNC=1 %command%" in your launch options (drop quotes, obviously)

Near identical frame rate as when running under windows 10 on the same machine.

Borderless window mode is best; there were some glitches when switching focus from/to fullscreen.

Required to run:
  cd ~/.local/share/Steam/steamapps/common/BorderlandsGOTYEnhanced/Binaries/Win64  ;
  mv Launcher.exe Launcher.exe.donotwant  ;
  ln -s BorderlandsGOTY.exe ./Launcher.exe
